    answer: "For a PSARA-compliant Pune transfer, request sight of the operator's PSARA Maharashtra State licence certificate and the individual driver's background verification documentation. PSARA 2005 requires agencies to conduct police verification of all security personnel. A properly licensed Pune operator will be able to produce both the agency licence and the individual's police verification clearance on request."
